    <h>fear</h>
    <p><g>fear</g>
        <en>man</en> is a masculine <a href="?xx=nouns/simple common_nouns">simple common
        noun</a>.</p>

    <section id="forms">
        <h>forms</h>
        <p>The principal parts of <g>fear</g> are – <ul>
                <li><m>fear</m> – nominative/dative singular, genitive plural</li>
                <li><m>fir</m> – genitive singular, nominative/dative plural</li>
            </ul>
        </p>
        <section id="definiteness">
            <h>definiteness</h>
            <p><ul>
                    <li>indefinite <ul>
                            <li>singular <ul>
                                    <li>nominative – <m>fear</m></li>
                                    <li>dative – le <m>fear</m></li>
                                    <li>genitive – ceann <m>fir</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                            <li>plural <ul>
                                    <li>nominative – <m>fir</m></li>
                                    <li>dative – le <m>fir</m></li>
                                    <li>genitive – cinn <m>fhear</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                        </ul></li>
                    <li>definite <ul>
                            <li>singular <ul>
                                    <li>nominative – <m>am fear</m></li>
                                    <li>dative – leis <m>an fhear</m></li>
                                    <li>genitive – ceann <m>an fhir</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                            <li>plural <ul>
                                    <li>nominative – <m>na fir</m></li>
                                    <li>dative – leis <m>na fir</m></li>
                                    <li>genitive – cinn <m>nam fear</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                        </ul></li>
                </ul></p>
        </section>
        <section id="number">
            <h>number</h>
            <p><ul>
                    <li>singular <ul>
                            <li>indefinite <ul>
                                    <li>nominative – <m>fear</m></li>
                                    <li>dative – le <m>fear</m></li>
                                    <li>genitive – ceann <m>fir</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                            <li>definite <ul>
                                    <li>nominative – <m>am fear</m></li>
                                    <li>dative – leis <m>an fhear</m></li>
                                    <li>genitive – ceann <m>an fhir</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                        </ul></li>
                    <li>plural <ul>
                            <li>indefinite <ul>
                                    <li>nominative – <m>fir</m></li>
                                    <li>dative – le <m>fir</m></li>
                                    <li>genitive – cinn <m>fhear</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                            <li>definite <ul>
                                    <li>nominative – <m>na fir</m></li>
                                    <li>dative – leis <m>na fir</m></li>
                                    <li>genitive – cinn <m>nam fear</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                        </ul></li>
                </ul></p>
        </section>
        <section id="case">
            <h>case</h>
            <p><ul>
                    <li>nominative <ul>
                            <li>indefinite <ul>
                                    <li>singular – <m>fear</m></li>
                                    <li>plural – <m>fir</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                            <li>definite <ul>
                                    <li>singular – <m>am fear</m></li>
                                    <li>plural – <m>na fir</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                        </ul></li>
                    <li>dative <ul>
                            <li>indefinite <ul>
                                    <li>singular – le <m>fear</m></li>
                                    <li>plural – le <m>fir</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                            <li>definite <ul>
                                    <li>singular – leis <m>an fhear</m></li>
                                    <li>plural – leis <m>na fir</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                        </ul></li>
                    <li>genitive <ul>
                            <li>indefinite <ul>
                                    <li>singular – ceann <m>fir</m></li>
                                    <li>plural – cinn <m>fhear</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                            <li>definite <ul>
                                    <li>singular – ceann <m>an fhir</m></li>
                                    <li>plural – cinn <m>nam fear</m></li>
                                </ul></li>
                        </ul></li>
                </ul></p>
        </section>
    </section>

